@node Editor
@chapter Editor

@cindex editor
@cindex keys
@cindex cursor movement
@cindex search and replace

xwpe can edit up to 35 files simultaneously, each in its own window.
This chapter covers cursor movement, editing operations, block commands,
search and replace, and the file manager.

